name: Shimizu Akari
description: A cheerful S-Rank Healer and member of the Blade Guild, known for her fiery battle axe and unyielding spirit. Raised in a devout household, Shimizu rebelled against tradition to protect her younger sister, Himari, and ultimately awakened her radiant powers during a life-threatening festival attack. She now fights to shine as brightly as the sun, carrying her sister’s hopes with her.

name: Thomas Andre
description: Thomas "Goliath," an S-Rank Hunter, wields monstrous power and brutal skill, believing in justice through overwhelming force.

name: Isla Wright
description: An A-Rank healer nicknamed “The Cursed Child,” uses tarot cards to guide her decisions and empower her allies. Once a reclusive figure, she found purpose after a fateful prediction led her to awaken her powers. Now, her mystical healing and protective spells make her a vital, if enigmatic, support for her team.

name: Gina
description: An assertive A-Rank Mage and a former solo hunter with a reputation for demanding things go her way, earning her the nickname "Veto Queen." Reluctant to trust others, she preferred working alone until an unexpected ally changed her perspective. Though still fiercely independent, she now joins dungeon raids with select teams, using her powerful gravitational and fire magic to control the battlefield.

name: Charlotte
description: The older of the twins, a master of Magic and Doll Summoning. She’s cunning, protective, and driven by her past at an orphanage with her sister Harper. In battle, she uses her dolls and dark magic to deal heavy damage and control enemies, all while staying focused on her mission to protect those she loves.

name: Harper
description: The younger of the twins, know for her mischievous pranks, and a member of the Helper's strike squad, Harper works alongside her sister Charlotte to track down the infamous serial killer, X, while raiding dungeons across England. Although Harper seems lighthearted and playful, she's driven by a deep desire for retribution following the tragic death of their beloved caretaker, Sister Millie.

name: Go Gunhee
description: Initially a successful businessman, his life changed after awakening extraordinary powers. Though aging and dealing with health issues, he became a crucial figure in managing the chaos brought by the gates and magic beasts. His leadership helped establish a system to protect hunters and maintain order. Even though he no longer fights, his dedication to the hunter community and his powerful presence as a National Level Hunter earned him the title "Heaven Beyond the Sky."

name: Han Se-Mi
description: An A-Rank Hunter and the youngest member of the Hunter Guild's B-Team strike squad. Despite her immense power and capability, she carries the heavy burden of caring for her four younger siblings after the disappearance of their parents. Known for her cheerful and nurturing personality, she serves as both the heart and shield of her team, with her ultimate goal is to ensure her siblings' happiness while searching for her lost family.

name: Amamiya Mirei
description: A focused and determined hunter, originally unawakened, she dreamed of standing beside the hunter who once saved her. After facing numerous challenges, Mirei finally awakens during a dungeon break, unlocking the powers of Oni Kuroha.

name: Yoo Soohyun
description: A talented A-Rank Hunter and model. Despite her natural aptitude and striking abilities, her first raid revealed a dangerous flaw: an uncontrollable adrenaline rush that made her a liability to her team. Haunted by her past and dubbed "the Time Bomb," Soohyun retired from active hunting but remains a fan-favorite for her fiery skills and complex story.

name: Meilin Fisher
description: A cheerful A-Rank Hunter and summoner with a water affinity, Meilin Fisher fights alongside her guardian spirit, Berry. Once a C-Rank hunter, her reawakening transformed her into a formidable force. Meilin’s journey from feeling out of place to finding strength in companionship embodies her unwavering determination and bond with her eternal companion.

name: Alicia Blanche
description: A 21-year-old leader of the French Justitia Guild; Alicia's rise to prominence came after her father's untimely death. Despite being a powerful S-Rank hunter, her reputation as the "Ice Witch" stems from a fateful raid where she was the sole survivor, leading to widespread condemnation. Driven by a thirst for justice and redemption, Alicia's main goal is to track down the enemy responsible for the massacre, reclaim her honor, and avenge her fallen comrades.

name: Cha Hae-In
description: An S-Rank Hunter and the vice guild master of the Hunters Guild, renowned for her unshakable resolve and masterful swordsmanship. Once a track-and-field prodigy, her life took an unexpected turn after her awakening. Now, she channels her competitive spirit into protecting the weak and striving for new heights as a Hunter.

name: Esil Radiru
description: Sometimes, she had the sinking feeling that she'd forgotten something terribly important. "What am I looking for? What should I be looking for" This stranger seemed to know the answer.

name: Choi Jong-In
description: Jong-In, "The Flame Emperor," is a strategic and powerful fire mage whose calm confidence and leadership strengthen his guild and the story.

name: Silver Mane Baek Yoonho
description: Baek Yoonho, the White Tiger Guild Master known as "Silver Mane," is a powerful hunter admired for his strength, leadership, and selfless dedication to others.

name: Baek Yoonho
description: His especially large stature and fierce, almost beast-like complexion gave off the impression that he was built to never lose to any fire. It was no wonder why people thought of him as a born fire-fighting machine.

name: Emma  Laurent
description: She stands out with her striking appearance—long, flowing hair and sharp, determined eyes that reveal a fierce will and intelligence. Emma is known for her exceptional combat skills and strategic mind, making her a formidable hunter in the dangerous world of dungeons and monsters. Despite the challenges she faces, Emma exudes confidence and remains focused on her goals, demonstrating both strength and resilience

name: Hwang Dongsoo
description: He is known for being selfish, murderous, and overconfident. He enjoys abusing his power and targeting those weaker than him1. Despite his despicable personality, he respects power above anything else

name: Lee Bora
description: She is known for her off-field support abilities, making her a valuable asset to any Dark-element lineup. Unlike other characters who engage enemies directly, Lee Bora excels at inflicting debuffs and supporting her teammates from a distance.

name: Lim Tae-Gyu
description: His relaxed expression on the court was a result of him being prepared for anything that could come his way. It was sometimes a misunderstanding for conceit, but it didn't bother him.

name: Min Byung-Gu
description: He decided he wasn't a nice person at all. He was just someone who wanted to be wanted, and his power gave him the means to do that. And his "mission?" Had been a smokescreen to prevent the world from seeing what he really was: a hypocrite.

name: Seo Jiwoo
description: A reluctant A-Rank Hunter with overwhelming strength she never wanted. Once an ordinary office worker, her awakening forced her into the Hunters Guild, where she trains tirelessly, hoping to regain a sense of normalcy.

name: Woo Jinchul
description: Jinchul worked hard to be able to stand in front of Go Gunhee, and when he did, he spoke about his aspiration with confidence. When he saw the hint of a smile on Go Gunhee's face, he knew his dream had a place there.

name: Anna Ruiz
description: Anna Ruiz excels at striking foes from afar with her poison-tipped arrows. Her abilities, amplified by high Attack and Water elements, make her indispensable in any team.

name: Han Song-Yi
description: Han Song-Yi is a highly skilled hunter, known for her fierce determination and exceptional combat prowess.

name: Hwang Dongsuk
description: Hwang Dongsuk is a tenacious B-Rank Hunter. Driven by jealousy and ambition, he often clashes with stronger hunters, showcasing his ruthlessness and thirst for power.

name: Jo Kyuhwan
description: Jo Kyuhwan is a skilled and determined hunter,  with his unyielding spirit and strategic mind, he stands out as a powerful ally in the battle against monsters.

name: Kim Chul
description: Kim Chul is a powerful and ruthless hunter whose strategic brilliance and relentless ambition make him a central and unforgettable character in the thrilling narrative.

name: Kim Sangshik
description: Kim Sangshik is a skilled hunter known for his strength, bravery, and determination, he tackles powerful foes and aids Jin-Woo in his quest.

name: Nam Chae-Young
description: She excels in dealing Water elemental damage and breaking enemies with skills like Ice Grenade and Icy Wind

name: Park Beom-Shik
description: He's a caring family man who returned to hunting to support his loved ones. Despite his uncertainties about his skills, he bravely faces dangers in dungeons alongside his friends

name: Park Heejin
description: A Mage-type hunter in the White Tiger Guild. Thanks to her unmatched survival instincts, she always knows which choice will keep her alive. She and Sung Jinwoo were both involved in the Red Gate incident.

name: Yoo Jinho
description: The second son of Yoo Myunghan, the president of Yoojin Construction. Jinho befriended Sung Jinwoo through a twist of fate and several raids. He is one of the few people that Sung Jinwoo fully trusts.

name: Tawata Kanae
description: Tawata Kanae is a powerful, resourceful hunter with a calm demeanor. Her tactical expertise and formidable strength make her an essential ally in dangerous battles.
weapon: The Path a Hero Must Take

name: Cid Kagenou
description: Cid Kagenou, also known as "The Dark Hero," is a strategic mastermind from The Eminence in Shadow, manipulating events from the shadows with cunning and charm.

name: Tanya Degurechaff
description: Tanya Degurechaff, from The Saga of Tanya the Evil, is a ruthless, brilliant mage and soldier, known for her strategic genius and cold, calculated demeanor.

name: Satella
description: Satella is a mysterious, enigmatic character from the Re:Zero series, known for her dark, ethereal presence, powerful abilities, and complex, unpredictable nature.

name: Wang Ling (王令)
description: Wang Ling is the reincarnation of an ancient immortal king with invincible existence and immeasurable powers far beyond his control, but now that he's sixteen he faces his greatest battle yet... the High School. His birthday is December 26, 4395

name: Kang Taeshik
description: Kang Taeshik, is a cunning and ambitious A-rank hunter with questionable morals. His underhanded methods and ruthless personality often lead him to clash with others, including Sung Jinwoo.

name: Lee Joohee
description: A timid B-Rank Healer and a member of the Hunters Association. She had no intention of becoming a hunter, but gave in to a fellow staff member's persistent badgering. She does hunting work as a volunteer, so she only participates in low-difficulty raids to help the weaker hunters.

name: Song Chiyul
description: Song Chi-Yul is a wise and experienced instructor. He mentors aspiring hunters, offering valuable guidance. Despite his older age, he possesses powerful combat abilities and unwavering resolve.

name: Goto Ryuji
description: Japan’s strongest S-Rank Hunter and Blade Guild master, is driven by duty over fame or fortune. Though not a National Level Hunter, his exceptional skill and leadership make him a formidable force. Beneath his conviction, he secretly longs for greater recognition.

name: Kiritsugu Emiya
description: Kiritsugu Emiya, also known as "The Magus Killer", is a mage from the Fate series, known for getting the job done by any means necessary.

name: Portgas D. Ace
description: Portgas D. Ace or "fire fist ace" was a pirate from One Piece, also the previous user of the Mera Mera no mi (flame-flame fruit)

name: Ryomen Sukuna
description: Ryomen Sukuna, also known as the King of Curses, is  central antagonist in Jujutsu Kaisen. He was considered the strongest jujutsu sorcerer in history. After death, he split his power into 20 cursed fingers, allowing him to become a cursed spirit himself.

name: Carl
description: "Carl-bot is a versatile and highly customizable Discord bot offering a wide range of features for managing and enhancing Discord servers."

name: Seorin
description: An administrative staff member with the Korean Hunters Association. She's an ordinary Hunters Association staff member by day, but by night, she handles secret missions.

name: Wick
description: I ain't John Wick. I am Wick

name: Yoshino Himekawa
description: puppet loli

name: Meliodas
description: Meliodas is known as the Dragon's Sin of Wrath. This is because he destroyed the Kingdom of Danafor in a fit of rage after a battle with Fraudrin. The world believed he had murdered the entire kingdom in his anger, though in reality, Fraudrin had already done so.

name: Gojo Satoru
description: He is the strongest special grade jujutsu sorcerer. Satoru is the pride of the Gojo Clan, the first person to inherit both Limitless and the Six Eyes in four hundred years. He is known as The Honor.

name: Cock
description: The Biggest
